@startuml
title Activity Diagram: AI Support Chat Workflow

start

:User submits a query on the support page;

:System sends the query to the Genkit AI flow;

:The Genkit flow calls the Google AI Service with the user's query;

:AI Service analyzes the query to understand intent;

if (Does the query require human intervention?) then (yes)
  :The AI response flags the conversation for escalation;
  :System notifies the user that a support agent will be in touch;
else (no)
  :The AI generates a helpful response;
  :System displays the AI response to the user;
endif

stop

@enduml
